      "text": [
        " \"لاَ بَأْسَ إِذَا كَانَ مِنْ طَعَامِكَ\" وَ سَأَلَهُ عَنْ مُؤَاكَلَةِ اَلْمَجُوسِيِّ فَقَالَ \"إِذَا تَوَضَّأَ فَلاَ بَأْسَ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.4222 - And Al-'Ays ibn Al-Qasim asked Imam (as): \"Regarding eating with a Jew or a Christian?\"\nImam (as) said: \"There is no harm if it is from your food.\"\nAnd he asked Imam (as) about eating with a Magian.\nImam (as) said: \"If he performs ablution, then there is no harm.\""
        ]
      }
    },
